### PoDebateRap API - HTTP Requests for Manual Testing
### Base URL for local development

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================================
### Health Checks
### ============================================================

### Overall Health Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Liveness Check (is the app running?)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

### Readiness Check (are all dependencies ready?)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/ready
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Rapper Endpoints
### ============================================================

### Get All Rappers
GET {{baseUrl}}/Rappers
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Rapper by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/Rappers/eminem
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Random Rapper
GET {{baseUrl}}/Rappers/random
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Topics Endpoints
### ============================================================

### Get Available Topics
GET {{baseUrl}}/Topics
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Random Topic
GET {{baseUrl}}/Topics/random
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Debate Endpoints
### ============================================================

### Start a New Debate
POST {{baseUrl}}/Debate/start
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "rapper1": "eminem",
    "rapper2": "tupac",
    "topic": "Who is the greatest rapper of all time?"
}

###

### Get Current Debate State
GET {{baseUrl}}/Debate/state
Accept: application/json

###

### Signal Audio Playback Complete
POST {{baseUrl}}/Debate/signal-audio-complete
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Reset Debate
POST {{baseUrl}}/Debate/reset
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### ============================================================
### News Endpoints
### ============================================================

### Get Trending Topics from News
GET {{baseUrl}}/News/trending
Accept: application/json

